<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Power is a relative term:<p>

Necro's do the most amount of damage over extended periods of time (DoT's and pets). They most certainly do not suck, they are just a bit more complex to play, and the shear amount of damage they can do doesn't seem to become evident until after lvl 20 or so. And they solo rather well compared to most other classes.<p>

Wizzie's do the most damage in a brief period of time. can't comment much on wizzies, i've never played one, but I wouldnt want to try and solo as one.<hr>Litermin Laplace<br>
Cleric of Bristlebane<br>
Errolisi Marr</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
