<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Will decline to enter the fray of "who is the best kiter".  Just want to counter one point posted in this thread.<p>

&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Myth_Darkbear<p>

&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Ohh yeah malise's sticking power ties strongly with Charisma so I wear a crude stein and of course always have a charisma buff on (109 charisma in total now). <p>

Charisma has ZERO effect on Malise/Malisement/Malosi sticking. None whatsoever.  Resists are determined by.... Your level versus MOB level, your skill on Alteration(which malise uses), and the MOBS Magic Resistance.  If you want the facts to back this statement up, see all the research done on this and other stats at the Shaman's Crucible.  www.eqforge.com/shaman<hr>lvl47 Shaman AC Monkey - Morell-Thule</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
